    <li id="cha-1_footnote-7">railstutorial.org/help <a class="arrow" href="#cha-1_footnote-ref-7">↑</a></li>
    <li id="cha-1_footnote-8">For example, to find the definition of a function called <code>foo</code>, you can do a global search for “def foo”. <a class="arrow" href="#cha-1_footnote-ref-8">↑</a></li>
    <li id="cha-1_footnote-9">c9.io/signup <a class="arrow" href="#cha-1_footnote-ref-9">↑</a></li>
    <li id="cha-1_footnote-10">learnenough.com/command-line <a class="arrow" href="#cha-1_footnote-ref-10">↑</a></li>
